#: ../../platform/faq.rst:2
msgid "Frequently Asked Questions"
msgstr "常见问题"

#: ../../platform/faq.rst:5
msgid "How to choose grid dimensions nx/ny/nz?"
msgstr "如何选择网格维度 nx/ny/nz？"

#: ../../platform/faq.rst:7
msgid "The grid dimensions nx/ny/nz should be determined based on the k-point density used in your first-principles calculation. Refer to the relevant VASP documentation for guidance on selecting appropriate grid dimensions."
msgstr "网格维度 nx/ny/nz 应根据第一性原理计算中使用的 k 点密度确定。请参阅相关 VASP 文档以获取选择合适网格维度的指导。"

#: ../../platform/faq.rst:9
msgid "Larger grids produce larger CHGCAR files and consume more GPU VRAM."
msgstr "更大的网格会生成更大的 CHGCAR 文件，并消耗更多 GPU 显存。"

#: ../../platform/faq.rst:12
msgid "Are nx/ny/nz required when uploading files?"
msgstr "上传文件时是否必须指定 nx/ny/nz？"

#: ../../platform/faq.rst:14
msgid "Yes. The ``/api/files/upload-structures`` endpoint requires ``nx``, ``ny``, and ``nz`` to be specified explicitly. No default values are provided, in order to prevent users from inadvertently using an unsuitable grid size."
msgstr "是的。``/api/files/upload-structures`` 接口要求显式指定 ``nx``、``ny`` 和 ``nz``。系统不提供默认值，以防止用户误用不合适的网格尺寸。"

#: ../../platform/faq.rst:17
msgid "If you upload a ``.db`` file directly (``/api/files/upload``), the grid settings already stored in the database are used."
msgstr "若直接上传 ``.db`` 文件（``/api/files/upload``），则使用数据库中已存储的网格设置。"

#: ../../platform/faq.rst:20
msgid "How to troubleshoot failed predictions?"
msgstr "预测失败时如何排查？"

#: ../../platform/faq.rst:22
msgid "Query the batch status to identify which tasks have failed"
msgstr "查询批次状态以确定哪些任务失败"

#: ../../platform/faq.rst:23
msgid "Inspect the backend log: ``tail -f /tmp/deepaw_backend.log``"
msgstr "查看后端日志：``tail -f /tmp/deepaw_backend.log``"

#: ../../platform/faq.rst:24
msgid "Check GPU status: ``curl http://localhost:8080/api/tasks/system/status``"
msgstr "检查 GPU 状态：``curl http://localhost:8080/api/tasks/system/status``"

#: ../../platform/faq.rst:27
msgid "Are molecular structures supported?"
msgstr "是否支持分子结构？"

#: ../../platform/faq.rst:29
msgid "Yes. When using the local CLI deployment, periodic boundary conditions must be disabled. When using the online version (deepaw.tech), setting periodic boundary conditions is not supported by default."
msgstr "支持。使用本地 CLI 部署时，需要禁用周期性边界条件。使用在线版本（deepaw.tech）时，默认不支持设置周期性边界条件。"

#: ../../platform/faq.rst:32
msgid "How to visualize CHGCAR files?"
msgstr "如何可视化 CHGCAR 文件？"

#: ../../platform/faq.rst:34
msgid "**VESTA** (free): open the CHGCAR file directly"
msgstr "VESTA（免费）：可直接打开 CHGCAR 文件"

#: ../../platform/faq.rst:35
msgid "**Ovito**: supports isosurface rendering"
msgstr "**Ovito**：支持等值面渲染"

#: ../../platform/faq.rst:36
msgid "**Web Frontend**: built-in Plotly 3D isosurface visualization"
msgstr "**Web 前端**：内置 Plotly 三维等值面可视化"

#: ../../platform/faq.rst:37
msgid "**Python**: plot manually using ASE + Plotly"
msgstr "**Python**：使用 ASE + Plotly 手动绘图"

#: ../../platform/faq.rst:40
msgid "What to do if GPU VRAM is insufficient?"
msgstr "GPU 显存不足时怎么办？"

#: ../../platform/faq.rst:42
msgid "Reduce the grid dimensions (e.g., from 64³ to 48³)"
msgstr "降低网格维度（例如从 64³ 降至 48³）"

#: ../../platform/faq.rst:43
msgid "Reduce the number of GPUs used simultaneously: ``export DEEPAW_GPUS=\"1,2\"``"
msgstr "减少同时使用的 GPU 数量：``export DEEPAW_GPUS=\"1,2\"``"

#: ../../platform/faq.rst:44
msgid "Check whether other processes are consuming VRAM: ``nvidia-smi``"
msgstr "检查是否有其他进程占用显存：``nvidia-smi``"

#: ../../platform/faq.rst:47
msgid "What is the difference between the two upload methods?"
msgstr "两种上传方式有何区别？"

